David Doyle (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Doyle_(actor) 0 David Fitzgerald Doyle (December 1, 1929 – February 26, 1997) was an American actor best known for his portrayal of John Bosley on the 1970s TV series Charlie's Angels.
